title: Tumi Voyageur Double-Zip Wristlet 481891 - Overview
description:
Tumi Voyageur Moroccan Blue Tile Print Double-Zip Wristlet - 481891-MOROCCAN BLUE TP
http://www.abt.com/product/96448/Tumi-481891MOROCCANBLUETP.html?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=video&utm_campaign=481891_20160419

From our stylish new Voyageur collection comes this slim wristlet trimmed with leather with a just the right amount of compartments for safeguarding small essentials. Toss it in your TUMI or slip it over your wrist and go.
Features:
• Primary Material: Fabric 
• Interior Features:
o 3 card slots
• Exterior Features:
o Front pocket with snap closure
o Back pocket with snap closure
o 2 zip compartments
o Open center compartment
